RPMEMLOG Documentation

1.0

RPMEMLOG (Real-time Printable Memory Log) is a lightweight logging library which stores logs into ring buffer while printing them into stdout in real-time. This software is distributed under the BSD (Berkeley Standard Distribution) license.
